746
00:47:40.940 --> 00:47:43.068
at iniwan akong may sugat sa ulo
at putol na braso.

747
00:47:43.693 --> 00:47:44.903
Nagtapos ang hukom

748
00:47:45.403 --> 00:47:49.616
